

Bertini Cascade Tests
---------------------

cascade.cc
----------

Tests G4InuclCollider for user determined projectiles, targets and energies.

To run:

copy directory cascade/test to your diectory
 
edit main() in cascade.cc by commenting out all but the routine you wish to 
run, e.g. testINCAll

gmake

../bin/$G4SYTEM/cascade    (to use default particle, target, energy)

or

../bin/$G4YSTEM/cascade runId nCollisions bulletType momZ A Z

Notes:  momZ is in MeV/c

        bulletType is 1 = proton
                      2 = neutron
                      3 = pi+
                      5 = pi-
                      7 = pi0


